The album 100% has 16 tracks, and this torrent also has 16 tracks. Nothing missing. Some tags need to be changed though, especially as there appear to be two No.6 tracks which is clearly wrong. The link on play.com is missing the first track "moonshine", but is not actually missing on the album. The person who put up the tracklist on that site obviously made a mistake. Thanks for this btw, bought the limited edition because it's such a great album, Long live Weller.

All this could be prevented though, by sparing a few minutes to sort out the titles BEFORE you upload a torrent...if you can't be arsed to do it  for us (the common mortals) do it out of respect for the modfather...!
